title: 2008–09 Czech Cup
text:
The 2008–09 <a href="Czech%20Cup">Czech Cup</a> was the sixteenth edition of the annual <a href="association%20football">football</a> knock-out tournament of the <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>. It began on 20 July 2008 with the preliminary round. The final was held on 27 May 2009.
Quarterfinals.
The first legs were played on 8 and 9 April 2009. The second legs were played on 22 and 23 April 2009.
Semifinals.
The first legs were played on 6 and 7 May 2009. The second legs were played on 13 May 2009.
